data.description: 3.5 ACRES zoned Rural Residential on paved road on Black Hammock Island!!   AMAZING PRICE for a GREAT LOT.  Close to boat ramp, 9A, and shopping at River City Marketplace.  No HOA, No CDD fees.  Boat and RV parking okay. Area will require Septic and Well. Only 15 min from Heckscher and 295. Duval County City Services, cable available. Great location close to town!  Black Hammock Island has it's own fire station 24-7.  The Island has a community center and basketball courts.  Most homeowners own golf carts and ride around the island.  Property is getting mowed.
